	(text_box "Make sure to place a small decoupling capacitor (typically $0.1\\,\\mu\\text{F}$ or a combination of $10\\,\\mu\\text{F}$ and $0.1\\,\\mu\\text{F}$) as close to the microphone's $V_{\\text{DD}}$ pin as physically possible to keep the power clean."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 27.94 142.24 0)
		(size 38.1 20.32)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
